downloadDescription: Release of the Resource Access Connector for DLC distribution.
detailsSection: This release includes the Resource Access Connector version 6.2406.2002, packaged as an executable installer. It enables secure certificate-based authentication and integration with Microsoft Intune environments. This version includes performance improvements and bug fixes for enhanced reliability.
systemRequirementsSection:
- Windows Server 2016 or later/iOS/Android
- Admin privileges for installation
- Internet connectivity for service registration
installInstructionSection:
. Download the installer.
2. Run the .exe as Administrator.
3. Follow the on-screen setup wizard.
4. After installation, verify service status and logs.
5. Refer to the deployment guide for tenant-specific configuration.
